---
title: "Lithium monotherapy associated longitudinal effects on resting state brain networks in clinical treatment of bipolar disorder"
collection: publications
category: manuscripts
excerpt: 'This prospective study investigates the within-person impact of lithium monotherapy on the brain connectome in bipolar disorder, finding that lithium had a normalizing effect on mania-related connectome indices proportional to symptom change.'
date: 2019-06-01
venue: 'Bipolar Disord'
paperurl: 'https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/30421491/'
citation: 'Spielberg JM, Matyi MA, Karne H, Anand A. (2019). &quot;Lithium monotherapy associated longitudinal effects on resting state brain networks in clinical treatment of bipolar disorder.&quot; <i>Bipolar Disord</i>. 21(4):361-371.'
---
